en_132249_0	All the schools in the Eastern Province function from 7.30 a.m. to 12 for nine days from tomorrow due to prevailing heat in the region, Eastern Provincial Council Education Minister Singaravelu Thandauthapani stated today.
en_132249_1	He said that due to prevailing heat the schools could not function beyond noon.
en_132249_2	He said the schools would follow this schedule till May 12.
